snippet.title: Wilmot Works It Out | Wishlist today on Steam!
snippet.description:
Coming to PC & Mac on October 23rd, 2024. Wishlist it today on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2060590/Wilmot_Works_It_Out/

Wilmot Works It Out is a puzzle building game about completing beautiful images and hanging them in your house. Complete a series of puzzles to unlock new customisation options for your house, including colours, wallpapers, bookcases, and cats. This house is going to feel like a home in no time at all! 

Twitter: https://x.com/wilmotsgame
https://wilmotworksitout.com/
